OL,3,COwners of collapsed building ordered
OL,4,Cto carry out repairs
OL,6,FCouncil bosses have ordered the owners
OL,7,Fof a collapsed city centre building to
OL,8,Fcarry out repairs - or face a #700,000
OL,9,Fbill.
OL,11,FThe derelict building, on Kirkgate in
OL,12,FLeeds, partially fell down in April.
OL,13,FPart of the road has been closed since.
OL,15,FThe government has now approved an
OL,16,Fapplication by Leeds City Council to
OL,17,Fissue an urgent works notice. It means
OL,18,Fthe authority can require the owners
OL,19,FCity Fusion to repair the building and
OL,20,Ffive others which are at risk of
OL,21,Fcollapse.
