OL,6,FIf the company fails to start work
OL,7,Fwithin 28 days, the council can
OL,8,Fcomplete the repairs itself and bill
OL,9,FCity Fusion for the cost, estimated at
OL,10,F#700,000.
OL,12,FDeputy council leader Jonathan Pryor
OL,13,Fsaid: "We recognise the situation on
OL,14,FLower Kirkgate has proved frustrating
OL,15,Ffor local businesses and residents
OL,16,Fand, as a council, we have been
OL,17,Fdetermined to find a solution.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
