OL,3,COwners of collapsed building ordered
OL,4,Cto carry out repairs
OL,6,F"I would once again like to thank
OL,7,Fpeople living and working in the area
OL,8,Ffor the patience they have shown over
OL,9,Frecent months."
OL,11,FMartin Hamilton, director of Leeds
OL,12,FCivic Trust, said: "This is welcome
OL,13,Fnews and we hope that this will ensure
OL,14,Fthat action is taken early in 2025."
OL,16,FKirkgate is one of the oldest streets
OL,17,Fin Leeds. Some of the properties have
OL,18,Fbeen renovated thanks to lottery
OL,19,Ffunding, but others remain in a state
OL,20,Fof disrepair.
