OL,4,Cto carry out repairs
OL,6,FThe civic trust said there had been an
OL,7,Fincrease in anti-social behaviour and
OL,8,Fa downturn in trade as a result and
OL,9,Fthere was a risk of further
OL,10,Fdeterioration over the winter if
OL,11,Furgent works were not completed.
OL,13,FMr Hamilton criticised the delay in
OL,14,Fgranting approval for the notice,
OL,15,Fsaying: "It does seem wrong that a
OL,16,Fcity the size of Leeds is not allowed
OL,17,Fto make these decisions locally and
OL,18,Fthat it took central government more
OL,19,Fthan four months to approve these
OL,20,Fmeasures.
